stacey 's mess this book is a really good book but it is n't the best . stacey 's dad tells her to pick a place to go on vacation to . she picks davis park because that 's where her boyfriend is working at . she brings claudia along.but then stacey spends all her time with robert and claudia 's mad . then kristy , shannon , and mary anne arrive for the fourth of july and claudia gets them on her side . now no one 's talking to stacey.can they ever be friends again ? read this book to find out